OL,3,CSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,5,GThe revamp of STV News looks good but
OL,6,Gis hardly worth the hyperbole of some
OL,7,Gclickbait articles.
OL,9,FIt is a simple evolution of the look
OL,10,Fof the programme.
OL,12,FIts last significant visual overhaul
OL,13,Fwas 10 years ago. Time alone means it
OL,14,Fis now time to freshen things up.
OL,16,FEverything changes but everything
OL,17,Fremains the same.
OL,19,FThe new set is still a very similar
OL,20,Fshade of blue. The signature tune has
OL,21,Fonly been remixed slightly.
