OL,3,CSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,5,FThe format of the programme ` revised
OL,6,Flast year when dual presentation from
OL,7,Fboth Glasgow and Edinburgh ended `
OL,8,Fremains the same.
OL,10,FThe advantage of the new set is that
OL,11,Fit looks more modern and allows more
OL,12,Fspace for reporters to join the
OL,13,Fpresenter.
OL,15,FBut I bet 90% of viewers will hardly
OL,16,Fnotice the changes in a couple of
OL,17,Fweeks. And this is how it should be.
OL,19,FThe days when regional news programmes
OL,20,Fgot brand new looks every two or three
OL,21,Fyears are thankfully gone.
