OL,3,CSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,5,FBy my reckoning there were five
OL,6,Fdistinct looks for what was then
OL,7,FScotland Today between 1986 and 1996.
OL,8,FEach change brought completely new
OL,9,Ftitles, music and sets plus
OL,10,Falterations to the format.
OL,12,FIn contrast News at Ten stayed
OL,13,Ffundamentally unchanged from 1967 to
OL,14,F1992. Each new look kept the core
OL,15,Felements and format, simply freshening
OL,16,Fup the appearance and taking advantage
OL,17,Fof new technology.
OL,19,FThere is no suggestion of any change
OL,20,Fto the format of STV News soon.
