OL,3,CSTV News: a new but familiar look
OL,5,FDropping the Edinburgh sub-opt would
OL,6,Fneed Ofcom approval.
OL,8,FSo would fundamental changes like an
OL,9,Fend to the separate programme for the
OL,10,Fformer Grampian region.
OL,12,FWhether they'd ever dare to record
OL,13,Fthis in Glasgow at 5pm ` aping some
OL,14,FEnglish regions ` is another question.
OL,16,FSo, all in all it's an attractive new
OL,17,Flook but one which will quickly become
OL,18,Fvery familiar.
